{"tid":1945952,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西班牙停用9000個中國製武漢病毒測試劑","createTime":"2020-03-27T11:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T11:01:53.000Z","uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2897c2406f0031b5cd60c0c938a4c6839e6180aa","tid":1945952,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/27/coronavirus-test-kits-withdrawn-spain-poor-accuracy-rate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Fmar%2F27%2Fcoronavirus-test-kits-withdrawn-spain-poor-accuracy-rate&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=a39c706d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/27/coronavirus-test-kits-withdrawn-spain-poor-accuracy-rate</a><br />\n<br />\n因測試劑準確檢測率只有三成，西班牙停用9000個中國製試劑。<br />\n中國官方回應指該生產商並無官方授權。<br />\n西班牙政府則強調該批試劑是經西班牙供應商採購，<br />\n並宣布本週將向中國購買約36.9億港元的各種抗疫物資。"}]}